data.description: If small town living is what you are searching for...take a look at this nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick home in the heart of Tecumseh. 2-car attached garage, sunroom (not included in square footage), storm cellar, cute gazebo and so much more. Home needs some TLC but is in very good condition (selling as is).
